la Stadium ODI matches|work= ESPNcricinfo|accessdate= 20 November 2012}}</ref>\n|37<ref>{{cite news|url= http://stats.espncricinfo.com/bangladesh/engine/records/team/match_results.html?class=3;id=2025;type=ground|title= Sher-e-Bangla Stadium T20I matches|work= ESPNcricinfo|accessdate= 20 November 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Zohur Ahmed Chowdhury Stadium]] ||[[Chittagong]] ||22,000 ||2006\n|17<ref>{{cite news|url= http://stats.espncricinfo.com/bangladesh/engine/records/team/match_results.html?class=1;id=1931;type=ground|title= ZAC Stadium Test matches|work= ESPNcricinfo|accessdate= 20 November 2012}}</ref>\n|19<ref>{{cite news|url= http://stats.espncricinfo.com/bangladesh/engine/records/team/match_results.html?class=2;id=1931;type=ground|title= ZAC Stadium ODI matches|work= ESPNcricinfo|accessdate= 20 November 2012}}</ref>\n|17<ref>{{cite news|url= http://stats.espncricinfo.com/bangladesh/engine/records/team/match_results.html?class=3;id=1931;type=ground|title= ZAC Stadium T20I matches|work= ESPNcricinfo|accessdate= 20 November 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Sylhet International Cricket Stadium]] ||[[Sylhet]] ||18,500 ||2014\n|1<ref>{{cite news|url=http://stats.espncricinfo.com/ci/engine/records/team/match_results.html?class=1;id=1564;type=ground|title= Sylhet Stadium Test matches|work= ESPNcricinfo|accessdate= 4 November 2018}}</ref>\n|4\n|7<ref>{{cite news|url= http://stats.espncricinfo.com/bangladesh/engine/records/team/match_results.html?class=3;id=1564;type=ground|title= Sylhet Stadium T20I matches|work= ESPNcricinfo|accessdate= 20 November 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n! colspan=7|Former Venues\n|-\n|[[Bangabandhu National Stadium]] ||[[Dhaka]] || 36,000 ||1955\n|17<ref>{{cite news|url= http://stats.espncricinfo.com/bangladesh/engine/records/team/match_results.html?class=1;id=475;type=ground|title= Bangabandhu Stadium Test matches|work= ESPNcricinfo|accessdate= 20 November 2012}}</ref>\n|58<ref>{{cite news|url= http://stats.espncricinfo.com/bangladesh/engine/records/team/match_results.html