nd 6 players were selected for white ball only contract.<ref>{{cite news |title=Mahmudullah, Mustafizur axed from Test contract list |url=https://www.cricbuzz.com/cricket-news/112651/mahmudullah-mustafizur-axed-from-test-contract-list |accessdate=9 March 2020 |work=Cricbuzz |language=en}}</ref>\n\nOn 10 March 2020, the contract list was published. The monthly salary cap was not increased while Category C and D was reintroduced. According to the new contract system, a player having contract for both format with two different contract grade, will be paid full salary for the higher grade and half salary will be given for lower grade, similarly a player having same contract grade for both format will be paid full salary for one format and half for the rest. [[Tamim Iqbal]] is the highest paid player who earns {{BDTConvert|6.3|l}} per month while [[Mushfiqur Rahim]] earns {{BDTConvert|6.2|l}} per month.<ref name=\"Contract 2020\">{{cite news |title=\u09b8\u09ac\u099a\u09c7\u09af\u09bc\u09c7 \u09ac\u09c7\u09b6\u09bf \u09a4\u09be\u09ae\u09bf\u09ae\u09c7\u09b0 \u09ac\u09c7\u09a4\u09a8, \u098f\u09b0\u09aa\u09b0 \u09ae\u09c1\u09b6\u09ab\u09bf\u0995 |url=https://www.prothomalo.com/sports/article/1644132/ |accessdate=10 March 2020 |work=\u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09a5\u09ae \u0986\u09b2\u09cb |language=bn}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=BCB`s new contract and cricketers salary |url=https://www.daily-bangladesh.com/english/BCBs-new-contract-and-cricketers-salary/38444 |accessdate=10 March 2020 |work=Daily Bangladesh |language=en}}</ref>\n\n;Key\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Symbol !! Meaning\n|-\n| S/N || Shirt number of the player in all formats\n|-\n| Contract || Two type of contract is given (X/X) for the player who has two different contract for Red and White ball.\n|- \n| style=\"background:red;\"| {{white|R/B}} || Red Ball contract\n|-\n| style=\"background:white;\"| W/B || White Ball contract\n|-\n| Format || denotes the player recently played in which particular format, not his